title: Typeform Surveys
text:
Below are the links to the Trust Her Contraceptive Services Report Forms, which are mandatory for all clinics in partnership with Trust Her to complete for every patient receiving contraceptive services. The table provided outlines the submission deadlines for these reports, segmented by the respective time periods.

* Review for the four quarters of the year are in January, April, July, and October

title: Clinic Response Review
text:
Access to the links below is restricted to designated staff members authorized by Trust Her for each respective clinic system. These links provide access to the Typeform survey responses submitted by the clinics. Survey responses are available for review exclusively during the first week of each clinicâ€™s specified update cadence. Please note that all responses will be securely erased following the final review date to ensure data privacy and compliance.
